a game which has now been exhibited at various events

375
00:21:38,291 --> 00:21:38,892
around the world.

376
00:21:39,272 --> 00:21:42,555
And I think through the course of the semester,

377
00:21:42,595 --> 00:21:44,057
Jenny really found a way.

378
00:21:46,790 --> 00:21:51,073
She really found a unified vision for these self-portrait games to the point where she

379
00:21:51,113 --> 00:21:56,476
now has this kind of internationally recognizable style in visual design and in game design.

