And I'm just showing this one as an example of how these one-week prototypes can become

386
00:22:25,853 --> 00:22:31,255
a platform that the students can use to build a bigger releasable project, either as part

387
00:22:31,275 --> 00:22:33,015
of their degree or after they graduate.

388
00:22:35,757 --> 00:22:39,638
The class is also a great place to try out ideas that there might not be room for in

